name: Donald Gaye Mccullen
description: I am a nice person and I try to treat people with honesty and fairness. I like to entertain at home, but do enjoy a night out every now and then. I am intelligent, good looking and have an off-beat sense of humor. I have been classified by my friend as a very kind,honest down to earth , confident, open Minded.faithful Person .I used to be a Party going Person. But now with God on my side I don’t seek the Lifestyle any More . I don’t smoke . Rarely drink
